001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.currentStatus.LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse;
007
008@HistoryLogProps(
009    opCode = 21,
010    displayName = "Extended Bolus Portion Complete",
011    internalName = "LID_BOLEX_COMPLETED",
012    usedByAndroid = true
013)
014public class BolexCompletedHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
015    
016    private int completionStatusId;
017    private LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse.BolusStatus completionStatus;
018    private int bolusId;
019    private float iob;
020    private float insulinDelivered;
021    private float insulinRequested;
022    
023    public BolexCompletedHistoryLog() {}
024    
025    public BolexCompletedHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int completionStatusId, int bolusId, float iob, float insulinDelivered, float insulinRequested) {
026        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, completionStatusId, bolusId, iob, insulinDelivered, insulinRequested);
027        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
028        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
029        this.completionStatusId = completionStatusId;
030        this.completionStatus = LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse.BolusStatus.fromId(completionStatusId);
031        this.bolusId = bolusId;
032        this.iob = iob;
033        this.insulinDelivered = insulinDelivered;
034        this.insulinRequested = insulinRequested;
035        
036    }
037
038    public int typeId() {
039        return 21;
040    }
041
042    /**
043     * <table border="1">
044     * <caption>Parsed fields for BolexCompletedHistoryLog:</caption>
045     * <tr><td><code>completionStatusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
046     * <tr><td><code>completionStatus</code></td><td><code>LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse.BolusStatus.fromId(completionStatusId)</code></td></tr>
047     * <tr><td><code>bolusId</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readShort(raw, 12)</code></td></tr>
048     * <tr><td><code>iob</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
049     * <tr><td><code>insulinDelivered</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
050     * <tr><td><code>insulinRequested</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22)</code></td></tr>
051     * </table>
052     */
053    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
054        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
055        this.cargo = raw;
056        parseBase(raw);
057        this.completionStatusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 10);
058        this.completionStatus = LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse.BolusStatus.fromId(completionStatusId);
059        this.bolusId = Bytes.readShort(raw, 12);
060        this.iob = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 14);
061        this.insulinDelivered = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 18);
062        this.insulinRequested = Bytes.readFloat(raw, 22);
063        
064    }
065
066    
067    /**
068     * <table border="1">
069     * <caption>Byte layout for BolexCompletedHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
070     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
071     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{21} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
084     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
085     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
086     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
087     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
088     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toFloat(iob) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
089     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
090     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
091     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
092     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinDelivered) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
093     * <tr><td>22</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
094     * <tr><td>23</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
095     * <tr><td>24</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
096     * <tr><td>25</td><td><code>toFloat(insulinRequested) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
097     * </table>
098     */
099    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, int completionStatus, int bolusId, float iob, float insulinDelivered, float insulinRequested) {
100        return Bytes.combine(
101            new byte[]{21, 0},
102            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
103            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
104            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(completionStatus), 
105            Bytes.firstTwoBytesLittleEndian(bolusId), 
106            Bytes.toFloat(iob), 
107            Bytes.toFloat(insulinDelivered), 
108            Bytes.toFloat(insulinRequested));
109    }
110    
111    public int getCompletionStatusId() {
112        return completionStatusId;
113    }
114    public LastBolusStatusAbstractResponse.BolusStatus getCompletionStatus() {
115        return completionStatus;
116    }
117    public int getBolusId() {
118        return bolusId;
119    }
120    public float getIob() {
121        return iob;
122    }
123    public float getInsulinDelivered() {
124        return insulinDelivered;
125    }
126    public float getInsulinRequested() {
127        return insulinRequested;
128    }
